ara acreditarem que a măe é a assassina e deve se entregar. Camila apresenta eloquentemente sua versăo dos eventos e entăo diz a Ezequiel que ele mentiu para fazer Patricia pagar por um crime que ela năo cometeu, assim como fizeram com sua măe." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3061000" grandparentArt="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentRatingKey="687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentThumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20596_1672531-portrait.jpg" grandparentTitle="Piel Salvaje" grandparentType="show" index="101" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" title="S01E101" userState="0"><Image alt="S01E101" type="coverArt" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E101" type="coverPoster" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20596_1672531-portrait.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E101" type="snapshot" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1776830944" duration="3061000" endsAt="1776834005" id="69de33bbe810768f822e07ca" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776849816" duration="3061000" endsAt="1776852877" id="69df8542ec0d2bce0f457cbf" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776871343" duration="3061000" endsAt="1776874404" id="69df8542ec0d2bce0f457cc6" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origi